title: Beautiful Studio Apartment
posting_body: ['Charles Apartments', 'Convenient access to the University of Minnesota, Hamline University, I-94, downtown St. Paul and Minneapolis, bus lines, light rails, dining, entertainment, and recreation.', "We are within blocks from the United Stadium, and Midway Shopping center with lots of shops: CVS, Milbern Clothing, At Home store, TJ Maxx, Dollar Tree, LA Fitness, Cub food, McDonald's, Culvers, Denny’s, and so much more.", 'Building Features:', 'o Building has new carpeting and paint', 'o Controlled Entry System', 'o Elevator', 'o Smoke-Free Building', 'o 24 Hour Maintenance Emergency Service', 'o Public Transportation', 'Property Amenities:', '• Off-Street Parking', '• Modern Appliances', '• Underground, Heated Parking - $100/month', '• Window Treatments Included', '• Air Conditioning', '• Storage Units Available - $10/month', '• On-Site Caretaker', '• Coin-Operated Laundry Facility', '• Recycling', 'Rent: $715', 'Security Deposit: $500 (on approved credit/income/rental history)', 'Application Fee: $50 fee per applicant (18 years or older)', 'Pet Fee: $250/pet deposit and $25/month pet rent per cat.', 'Allowed up to 2 cats.', '*Security deposit and application fee(s) are due at the time of application to hold your requested home', 'Visit our website below for more information.', '<URL>', 'Please include you contact information.']
